## Bundled Components

The `src/sci_html/integrations/figure/` directory contains code derived from
the `sci-figure` project, which is licensed under AGPL-3.0-or-later. When
distributing this package with the figure extraction integration included,
the AGPL-3.0 terms apply to the combined work.

If you wish to use only the core deck generation (parser, renderer, templates)
without the figure extraction integration, those components are available under
the MIT license above.
